### Install latest Next.js and run dev with Turbopack

Source: https://github.com/vercel/next.js/blob/canary/docs/01-app/02-guides/local-development.mdx

Update Next.js to the latest version to access performance improvements and use Turbopack as the default bundler for development. Turbopack provides significant performance benefits over webpack for local development.

```bash
npm install next@latest
npm run dev  # Turbopack is used by default
```

