### Next.js package.json Scripts with Explicit Turbopack Flags (Before v16)

Source: https://github.com/vercel/next.js/blob/canary/docs/01-app/02-guides/upgrading/version-16.mdx

This example illustrates how a `package.json` script might have been configured in Next.js versions prior to v16 to explicitly enable Turbopack for development and build processes using the `--turbopack` flag.

```json
{
  "scripts": {
    "dev": "next dev --turbopack",
    "build": "next build --turbopack",
    "start": "next start"
  }
}
```

