### Configure Turbopack in Next.js (15 & 16)

Source: https://github.com/vercel/next.js/blob/canary/docs/01-app/02-guides/upgrading/version-16.mdx

Demonstrates how to configure Turbopack in Next.js, showing the transition from `experimental.turbopack` in Next.js 15 to the top-level `turbopack` option in Next.js 16 for `next.config.ts` files. This configuration allows developers to specify Turbopack-specific options.

```typescript
import type { NextConfig } from 'next'

// Next.js 15 - experimental.turbopack
const nextConfig: NextConfig = {
  experimental: {
    turbopack: {
      // options
    },
  },
}

export default nextConfig
```

```typescript
import type { NextConfig } from 'next'

// Next.js 16 - turbopack at the top level of nextConfig
const nextConfig: NextConfig = {
  turbopack: {
    // options
  },
}

export default nextConfig
```

