### Large Module Export with Heavy Dependency - JavaScript

Source: https://github.com/vercel/next.js/blob/canary/docs/01-app/03-api-reference/08-turbopack.mdx

Example demonstrating a module that exports both a heavy-dependent function and a constant value. This code illustrates the gap in Turbopack's tree-shaking compared to Webpack's Inner Graph Optimization, where unused imports cannot be eliminated automatically.

```javascript
import heavy from 'some-heavy-dependency.js'

export function usesHeavy() {
  return heavy.run()
}

export const CONSTANT_VALUE = 3
```

